Package: panelforest
Title: Declarative and Modular Forest Plots
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Zhiyuan Xu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Zhiyuan Xu <hangzhouliuhaoran@163.com>
Authors@R: c(person("Zhiyuan", "Xu", email = "hangzhouliuhaoran@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Create tidy-style forest plots with declarative layouts,
    modular panel builders, and composable rendering based on 'ggplot2'
    and 'patchwork'. The package supports text, bar, dot, and confidence
    interval panels together with row-level structural controls such as
    stripes, group rows, summary rows, and horizontal separators.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    grid,
    patchwork,
    rlang
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vdiffr
VignetteBuilder:
    knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
NeedsCompilation: no
